name: Seasonal variation of the zooplankton community at Gazi, Lamu and Malindi (Kenya) sampled between 1990 and 1992
description: Copepoda species list, zooplankton densities and measurement of environmental variables at Gazi, Malindi and Lamu sampled between March and December 1992. The data were digitized by VLIZ from the original report: Osore, M. K. W. (1994). A study of the zooplankton of Gazi Bay, Kenya andthe adjecent waters: community structure and seasonal variation. MSc Thesis. Universiteit Gent: Ghent. 112 pp.
